  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a zombie apocalypse, your pizzeria may be the last haven of the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cook delicious pizzas, run over zombies, and deliver ultimate taste to survivors!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventure and mouth-watering pizzas await you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But you still don't have a clue what to do?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here are brief guides! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Step 1. Make delicious pizzas🍕</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/d9baef9562e1ccaf1bf5e1ef0900cbe6.poster.avif?t=1762586772\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/d9baef9562e1ccaf1bf5e1ef0900cbe6.webm?t=1762586772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/d9baef9562e1ccaf1bf5e1ef0900cbe6.mp4?t=1762586772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You are the owner of a pizzeria. Gather various ingredients and make pizza for the survivors. The path is complicated, so think about your route and take orders.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Step 2. Deliver to customers😍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/f1840834b6376a6a849d8c31a5328ad9.poster.avif?t=1762586772\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/f1840834b6376a6a849d8c31a5328ad9.webm?t=1762586772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/f1840834b6376a6a849d8c31a5328ad9.mp4?t=1762586772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You'll need to drive a sturdy car to make your deliveries through the hordes of zombies, and even in an apocalyptic world, you'll need to do it quickly and accurately! Zombies get stronger over time, so don't forget to upgrade or buy a good vehicle.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Step 3. Manage your pizzeria🏪</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/0090cb1d820f4f64dd70bd46095a97cc.poster.avif?t=1762586772\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/0090cb1d820f4f64dd70bd46095a97cc.webm?t=1762586772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/0090cb1d820f4f64dd70bd46095a97cc.mp4?t=1762586772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>There's a lot more to keep an eye on to make your store successful besides deliveries, including ratings, competitors who don't like pizza, upgrading base and vehicles, exploration, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can you make your pizzeria successful in the zombie apocalypse? It's up to you!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a zombie apocalypse, your pizzeria may be the last haven of the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cook delicious pizzas, run over zombies, and deliver ultimate taste to survivors!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventure and mouth-watering pizzas await you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But you still don't have a clue what to do?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here are brief guides! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Step 1. Make delicious pizzas🍕</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/d9baef9562e1ccaf1bf5e1ef0900cbe6.poster.avif?t=1762586772\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/d9baef9562e1ccaf1bf5e1ef0900cbe6.webm?t=1762586772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/d9baef9562e1ccaf1bf5e1ef0900cbe6.mp4?t=1762586772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You are the owner of a pizzeria. Gather various ingredients and make pizza for the survivors. The path is complicated, so think about your route and take orders.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Step 2. Deliver to customers😍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/f1840834b6376a6a849d8c31a5328ad9.poster.avif?t=1762586772\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/f1840834b6376a6a849d8c31a5328ad9.webm?t=1762586772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/f1840834b6376a6a849d8c31a5328ad9.mp4?t=1762586772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You'll need to drive a sturdy car to make your deliveries through the hordes of zombies, and even in an apocalyptic world, you'll need to do it quickly and accurately! Zombies get stronger over time, so don't forget to upgrade or buy a good vehicle.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Step 3. Manage your pizzeria🏪</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/0090cb1d820f4f64dd70bd46095a97cc.poster.avif?t=1762586772\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/0090cb1d820f4f64dd70bd46095a97cc.webm?t=1762586772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937920/extras/0090cb1d820f4f64dd70bd46095a97cc.mp4?t=1762586772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>There's a lot more to keep an eye on to make your store successful besides deliveries, including ratings, competitors who don't like pizza, upgrading base and vehicles, exploration, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can you make your pizzeria successful in the zombie apocalypse? It's up to you!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
